body.p:
The agent configuration, relying on basic key/value pairs, takes place in different locations depending on your operating system and the installation mode:


Windows: in the HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/SOFTWARE/FusionInventory-Agent section of the Windows registry;

Mac OS X: in the opt/Contents/Resources/agent.cfg file;

UNIX/Linux: in the /etc/fusioninventory/agent.cfg file;

Prebuilt: the agent.cfg configuration file is located in the package root directory.
